title: Jerron Paxton and Dennis Lichtman in Residence: 1920's Pop
description: Before rock, soul, and R&B took over the airwaves, pop music celebrated the sounds of jazz, and the roots of swing and big band. With music by Irving Berlin, Walter Donaldson, and more, go back in time and hear what your ancestors were telling all of their friends about. Part of Jerron Paxton and Dennis Lichtman in Residence.
address: Symphony Space, 2537 Broadway & 95th Street, NY, NY 10025
